	<p><font face="verdana, arial, helvetica" size="2" color="#FFFFFF">Perhaps if there were only a "$XX is needed per month to keep the site running - total donations last month: $YY".  This could be manually updated to require human time, but no particular resources to accomplish, and could at least give us a rough idea of where donating stands.  I think a lot of people get by with the 'Oh well, someone else will donate' line of thought and never realize just how rare it is.</font></p>
	
